::KitKat::

She looked up at War. "Tell me about him. Tell me about Destructor. 
And why in the matrix would he like me?"  She didn't really know 
anything about his past, but she also was never one to think that any 
bot in thier right mind would ever like her that way.  She had always 
concidered herself just a wolf bot and nothing special.
